t: (DEUS revealed HIC BENE Hadith; book est consistent points AMBO VIA CAELUM Hell)! skins de those reverence their Dominus cringe therefrom tunc their skins their hearts soften up deus message Such est deus guidance; He bestows it upon whoever testimentum guided Prout pro those sent astray DEUS nihil guide them